                                 <locus target="#50r">fol. 50r</locus> ዘሰኔ: <locus target="#54v">fol. 54v</locus> ዘነሐሴ: <locus target="#61v">fol. 61v</locus>
                              ዘመስከረም: <locus target="#65v">fol. 65v</locus> ዘጥቅምት: <locus target="#68r">fol. 68r</locus> ዘኅዳር: <locus target="#73r">fol.
                                 73r</locus> ዘታሕሣሥ: <locus target="#76v">fol. 76v</locus> [ዘ]ጥር:
                                 <locus target="#82r">fol. 82r</locus> [ዘ]ሐምሌ: <locus target="#88r">fol. 88r</locus> ጥ[sic]ጥር and ዘዘወትር: <locus target="#94r">fol.
                                 94r</locus> ዘዘወትር፡: <locus target="#96v">fol. 96v</locus>. - ዘቅድስት፡
