                           <desc>- Ommitted words or letters added interlineally: e.g., fols. 13ra, 14rb, 18vb, 25vb, 27ra, 36va, 73vb, 119rb, 122rb. - Recent notes in pen in the upper margin of fols. 10r and 53r. - Cotton thread is inserted at the edge of <locus target="#106">fol.  106</locus>.</desc>
                        </item>
