                  <provenance>Many names are mentioned in the supplication
                     formulas ("her servants" and "her maids"), e.g. Gabra ʾƎgziʾabǝḥer, Walda
                     Gabrǝʾel and Wälattä Yoḥannǝs, Walatta ʾIyasus (<locus target="#23ra">23ra</locus>); Walda Gabrǝʾel, Gabra Śǝllāse with Walatta Ḥǝwät, Walatta
                     Gärima (<locus target="#34rb">34rb</locus>); Gabra Ḥawarya (<locus target="#34va">34va</locus>, 45ra) and Walatta ʾƎgziʾ (<locus target="#45ra">45ra</locus>); Walatta Mikāʾel and Takla Mikāʾel (<locus target="#37va">37va</locus>, 94ra); Walda Libānos and Wälattä ʾIyasus (<locus target="#76va">76va</locus>, 130rb); Walatta Takla Hāymānot, Ḫāyla Māryām
                     and Gabra Mikāʾel (<locus target="#130r">130r</locus>).</provenance>
